description.en:
GarudaSwap.Finance is a brand new, audited, next generation yield farm on BSC.

Highlighted features of GarudaSwap are Innovative tokenomics, Anti whale,  Harvest lock-up to prevent token dumping, migrator code removed and 3% referral programme.

GarudaSwap.finance aim to be long live project, with low initial supply, Automatic Liquidity with 8% reflection tax, and safe to user as audited by Techrate and Certik (processing).
